{% load filters %}
Hello {{ receiver.first_name }},

You have received this auto generated email because you are the leader of VPAC Project {{ project.pid }}.
We would appreciate it if you could take a minute or so to check the data below to keep our records straight and ensure that your quota is being used appropriately. 

Project: {{ project.pid }}
------------------------------
Title: {{ project.name }}
Institute: {{ project.institute }}
Project Leader: {{ project.leader }}
Telephone: {{ project.leader.telephone }}

Users
-------------{% for m in members %}
{{ m.username }}\t\t{{ m }}{% endfor %}


You appear to have {{ members.count }} user{{ members|pluralize }} authorised under this project.
Please visit {{ project_users_site }} or email help@vpac.org if any of these users should no longer have access under your project. You probably should also advise what should happen to their files.

Usage (activity between {{ start }} and {{ end }})
------------------------------------------------------------------------{% for u in usage_list %}
{{ u.user.username }}\t\t{{ u.user }}\t\tusage: {{ u.usage|timeformat}}\t\tjobs:{{ u.jobs }}{% endfor %}

For more information about your projects usage please see {{ usage_site }}

You can log in and view edit your details at any time by going to {{ site }}

Thanks for your time,

VPAC Accounts
